definitions.definition: A card game similar to rummy and played using two packs , where the object is to meld groups of the same rank .
A meld of seven cards in a game of canasta.

main_definition: ( uncountable , games , card games ) A card game similar to rummy and played using two packs , where the object is to meld groups of the same rank .
secondary_definitions: ( countable , card games ) A meld of seven cards in a game of canasta.
